        "new_string": "        # For ForeignKey fields with a non-pk to_field, extract the value using\n        # the target field instead of the attname (which would be the pk).\n        if isinstance(f, ForeignKey):\n            remote_field_is_pk = (\n                f.remote_field.field_name == f.remote_field.model._meta.pk.name\n            )\n            if not remote_field_is_pk:\n                # Get the related object and extract the value from the to_field\n                related_obj = getattr(instance, f.name, None)\n                if related_obj is not None:\n                    data[f.name] = getattr(related_obj, f.remote_field.field_name)\n                else:\n                    data[f.name] = None\n            else:\n                data[f.name] = f.value_from_object(instance)\n        else:\n            data[f.name] = f.value_from_object(instance)",
